onfraternity of Misericórdia in the Early Modern Portuguese Seaborne Empire: Goa, Salvador da Bahia, Nagasaki.” In ''Neue Zeitschrift für Missionswissenschaft'' 58, no. 4 (2002): 241-60. *''Christian Theology of Martyrdom and Women Martyrs in Early Modern Japan'' (In Progress).
